{"tid":420312,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"HK Express: 18班取消航班為不受歡迎航線","createTime":"2017-10-01T09:38:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-11T18:40:28.000Z","uid":6604,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"552b6ed2134a3447dbdd016de81fac5ce4f0912d","tid":420312,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T09:38:14.000Z","msg":"廉航香港快運航空，突然在國慶及中秋假期取消今日至8日往返香港與日本關西、名古屋及韓國首爾仁川共18個定期航班，近2000乘客受影響。香港快運行政總裁安浩恩下午回應記者，指上月26日仍未能確保有足夠後備機組人員，為顧及航空安全，所以取消黃金周假期18班較不受歡迎航班。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d929bd91900ea0263fa98e7fd79acd0487e1c204","tid":420312,"uid":24168,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T09:41:02.000Z","msg":"Cut 你班機係因為你係不受歡迎旅客"},{"pid":"b2dcef09755f3f2ebea8efa01437a536b63f4654","tid":420312,"uid":11805,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T09:43:26.000Z","msg":"係咪翻譯亂屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點會咁講野 弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a6b50dc330ccf8fd613d87af70f76516767dda7","tid":420312,"uid":25635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T09:44:02.000Z","msg":"係咪顧客對服務滿意度最不受歡迎咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef3127e782338d08bc8e9acda05336904add6db5","tid":420312,"uid":11805,"like":7,"dislike